Create detailed documentation of all data objects exchanged between systems, including JSON schemas or class diagrams. Document all events from both systems that affect the other, including event names, payload structures, and propagation rules. Define data validation rules, transformation requirements, and error handling procedures for data exchange. Identify potential performance bottlenecks in the data flow and suggest mitigation strategies.
